parameters.name: blobParts
parameters.description: Array of ArrayBuffer, Blob, string, or any typed array. Any other type will be stringified. Strings are encoded as UTF-8.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name or path of the file

parameters.name: options
parameters.description:
`type` represents the MIME type of the blob content. Defaults to empty string.
`lastModified` is a unix timestamp of the last known modification of the file. Defaults to the current time.

description: Represents raw data of a given type and name.

lastModified.description: Unix timestamp of the last known modification of the file
